food_charges = float(input("the charges of the food: $"))
the charges of the food: $70
>>> tips = food_charges * 0.18
>>> sales_tax = food_charges * 0.07
>>> total_amount = food_charges + tips + sales_tax
>>> print(f"\nFood charge: ${food_charges:.2f}")

Food charge: $70.00
>>> print(f"Tip (18%): ${tips:.2f}")
Tip (18%): $12.60
>>> print(f"Sales Tax (7%): ${sales_tax:.2f}")
Sales Tax (7%): $4.90
>>> print(f"Total Amount: ${total_amount:.2f}")
Total Amount: $87.50
